{"word":"G4152 - πνευματικός - pneumatikós - pnyoo-mat-ik-os' - Spiritual","slug":"G4152","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">πνευματικός</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>pneumatikós"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>pnyoo-mat-ik-os'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Spiritual"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03C0;&#x03BD;&#x03B5;&#x03C5;&#x03BC;&#x03B1;&#x03C4;&#x03B9;&#x03BA;&#x03BF;&#x0301;&#x03C2; - pneumatikos</b> - <i>phyoo-mat-ik-os'</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G4151\">G4151</a>; <i>non-carnal</i>, that is, (humanly) <i>ethereal</i> (as opposed to gross), or (daemoniacally) a <i>spirit</i> (concretely), or (divinely) <i>supernatural</i>, <i>regenerate</i>, <i>religious</i>: - spiritual. Compare <a href=\"#/G5591\">G5591</a>."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1606\">G1606</a>, <a href=\"#/G2315\">G2315</a>, <a href=\"#/G4151\">G4151</a>, <a href=\"#/G4153\">G4153</a>, <a href=\"#/G4154\">G4154</a>"}]}